2.3 Metric Definitions (Stored in studentYearMetrics)
All metrics are computed on session submission and aggregated.

Avg Raw Score %
For each run:
rawPercent = (obtainedMarks / totalMarks) × 100
Year aggregation:
avgRawScorePercent = mean(rawPercent across runs)

Avg Accuracy %
For each run:
accuracyPercent = (correctAnswers / attemptedQuestions) × 100
Year aggregation:
avgAccuracyPercent = mean(accuracyPercent across runs)

Phase Adherence %
For each run:
phaseDeviation =
|actualPhaseTime - recommendedPhaseTime| / recommendedPhaseTime

phaseAdherenceRun =
100 - (mean phaseDeviation × 100)
Year:
avgPhaseAdherence = mean(phaseAdherenceRun)

Easy Neglect Rate %
Per run:
easyAttemptRate = easyAttempted / easyTotal

if easyAttemptRate < threshold:
   mark easyNeglectRun = 1
else:
   easyNeglectRun = 0
Year:
easyNeglectRate =
(sum easyNeglectRun / totalRuns) × 100

Hard Bias Rate %
ExpectedHardRatio:
expectedHardRatio =
totalHardQuestions / totalQuestions
DeviationAllowance:
0.10 × expectedHardRatio
Hard bias if:
studentHardRatio >
(expectedHardRatio + deviationAllowance)
Year:
hardBiasRate =
(runsWithHardBias / totalRuns) × 100

Behaviour Tag Summary
For each run compute normalized scores:
rushScore
overextensionScore
phaseDriftScore
impulsivityScore
Select highest per run.
Year summary:
mostFrequentTag

Guess Rate %
Per run:
if timeSpent < (minTime × guessFactor)
AND incorrect:
   mark guess
Difficulty-specific guessFactor:
    • Easy: 0.5
    • Medium: 0.6
    • Hard: 0.7
Run guessRate:
guesses / totalAttempted
Year:
avgGuessRate = mean(guessRate)

Risk Score
Normalized components 0–1.
riskScore =
0.30 × guessRate +
0.20 × phaseDeviation +
0.20 × easyNeglectRate +
0.15 × hardBiasRate +
0.15 × consecutiveWrongRate
Convert:
normalizedRiskScore = riskScore × 100

Discipline Index
disciplineIndex = 100 - normalizedRiskScore

Controlled Mode Performance Delta
If ≥ 3 runs in each mode:
delta =
avgRawPercentControlled -
avgRawPercentUncontrolled
Else null.

Execution Stability Flag
stdDev = standardDeviation(rawPercent across runs)
Bands:
    • Low → Stable
    • Medium → Moderate
    • High → Unstable

